title: Austromitra gradusspira
text:
Austromitra gradusspira is a <a href="species">species</a> of <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a>, a <a href="marine%20%28ocean%29">marine</a> <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a>, in the <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Costellariidae">Costellariidae</a>, the ribbed miters.
Distribution.
This species occurs in South Africa (country).
